{"tid":1236502,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［耶撚老鼠屎］撐送中 笑烈士都可以做校長？","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T11:17:18.000Z","uid":228907,"like":80,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bf50d528d14a11a5a20ba010f2c2bee39723472a","tid":1236502,"uid":228907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借朋友acc：<br />\n<br />\n我細佬今年六年級<br />\n頭先食飯聽佢講<br />\n佢學校（荃葵青區嗰頭 有宗教）個校長<br />\n今朝竟然用mic對全校師生發表偉論<br />\n話「<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你冇犯法 唔洗擔心修例咖喎</span>」<br />\n仲迫學生講喺電視新聞見到咩畫面<br />\n然後引導佢地話「示威者打警察」<br />\n佢問「<span style=\"color: red;\">有無人見到示威者用磚頭擲警察呀？</span>」<br />\n完全係以偏概全<br />\n黑警用橡膠槍又唔見佢講？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有 佢話：<br />\n叫學生唔好信新聞講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最嬲係咩？<br />\n係佢話：烈士係<span style=\"color: red;\">無啦啦跳落街</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">叫學生唔好學佢咁唔珍惜生命</span><br />\n<br />\n屌佢影衰晒耶撚<br />\n明明今舖耶撚企到咁前<br />\n佢係咪日日淨係睇cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5a9f1e6274f169ac26dbd5a3ea354ef2ea4e9972","tid":1236502,"uid":41901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"即係邊間?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48de6fdda7f2e59a5e0206c7103b66c68d0d82f0","tid":1236502,"uid":106958,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0708cf04eedc89126584e8ae6694edf54ca48fc3","tid":1236502,"uid":59922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"38718f71346b3a69e3d50fd4cb1742784d5769ff","tid":1236502,"uid":228907,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:49: